title: Imposter Syndrome with Sara May
description: Sara May makes going blonde look easy. She's the queen of lifting and level 10s are what she has built her reputation on. But even when you're top of your game, it's easy to feel like you don't belong there. Imposter Syndrom is REAL and we're talking about how it makes us feel and how we combat it!
